{"tid":1930874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港關係法】支那外交部，限制美國記者在香港採訪！","createTime":"2020-03-18T00:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T05:02:12.000Z","uid":37661,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"509462dc81b1fc15b0c280ca211e0fc3bb12a158","tid":1930874,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T00:39:28.000Z","msg":"外交部要求五美媒申報人員及財務等資料  <br />\n<br />\n52分鐘前  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】外交部凌晨宣布，即日起要求五間美國媒體申報人員及財務資料，並要求三份報章十日內交還年底前到期的美籍記者證。  <br />\n<br />\n外交部表示，為反制美方打壓中國媒體，即日起要求紐約時報、華爾街日報、華盛頓郵報等五間媒體駐華分社申報境內工作人員、財務、經營以及擁有的房產資料，又要求三份報章申報證件在年底前到期的美籍記者名單，十日內交還記者證，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他們今後亦不得在中國包​​括港澳地區採訪。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=384704&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D384704%26refer%3DShare&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzBzDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=8a93119c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D384704%26refer%3DShare&h=f5201e10\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=384704&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n一國兩制？港人治港？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8d003349be5f0a2c9a4b8142c29e27bdd500c2","tid":1930874,"uid":331973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T00:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/VigorousFocusedBabirusa-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FVigorousFocusedBabirusa-size_restricted.gif&h=6745a88b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83dca41165f07a2a19af8247b8fe45e3801e3b28","tid":1930874,"uid":10503,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"repl